{"tid":1331959,"cid":21,"subCid":2,"title":"《玫瑰玫瑰我愛你》原唱姚莉離世，享年96歲","createTime":"2019-07-19T06:38:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T07:35:59.000Z","uid":35221,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"fd7a784687c342955307c286677c03e63bb74521","tid":1331959,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T06:38:41.000Z","msg":"《玫瑰玫瑰我愛你》原唱姚莉離世　享年96歲<br />\n07月19日(五) 13:47<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/jOstKUVj4mQ/hqdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FjOstKUVj4mQ%2Fhqdefault.jpg&h=d2764e32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n姚莉<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/1/1d/China_singing_stars_1940s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fcommons%2F1%2F1d%2FChina_singing_stars_1940s.jpg&h=84c3dfa1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n左起為：白虹、姚莉、周璇、李香蘭、白光、祁正音<br />\n<br />\n一代歌后、《玫瑰玫瑰我愛你》原唱姚莉今晨離世，享年96歲，其好友邵音音亦在社交網發文證實姚莉死訊。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190719/photo/bkn-20190719134749239-0719_00862_001_03p.jpg?20190719141324\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190719%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190719134749239-0719_00862_001_03p.jpg%3F20190719141324&h=f5888c78&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190719/mobile/bkn-20190719134749239-0719_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20190719%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190719134749239-0719_00862_001.html&d=4e%2FpP7P6HSNE6mjGPWQpDcZCnWmYDHHppvVe94ioujI%3D&h=0b35934f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20190719/mobile/bkn-20190719134749239-0719_00862_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n姚莉原名姚秀雲，是上海灘時期知名女歌手之一，與周璇、白虹、白光、龔秋霞、李香蘭、吳鶯音等齊名，並稱為1940年代上海歌壇七大歌星。姚莉是香港1950年代最叱吒風雲的歌后，是多位歌后的偶像，包括鄧麗君、徐小鳳、潘迪華等。代表歌曲有《玫瑰玫瑰我愛你》、《得不到的愛情》、《春風吻上我的臉》、《蘇州河邊》、《恭喜恭喜》等。<br />\n<br />\n《玫瑰玫瑰我愛你》這首歌更被美國歌手法蘭基萊恩（Frankie Laine）翻唱為英文版本的《Rose, Rose, I Love You》，姚莉的中文原版打進美國壁報（Billboard）流行榜第3位，成為首位打入美國音樂流行榜的華人歌星。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n姚莉2012年曾來馬出席由本地歌手楊偉漢主辦的《姚莉玫瑰傳奇音樂劇》，結束一連10場的演出後，姚莉於2012年7月2日特地於《星洲日報》禮堂舉行《姚莉玫瑰傳奇交流會》，吸引大批樂齡歌迷，包括視障朋友前來捧場，場面多次失控。現場40本《姚莉──永遠綻放的玫瑰》自傳也被歌迷一掃而空，當時90歲高齡的姚莉親自將售書所得的4000令吉捐給星洲&ldquo;希望閲讀基金會&rdquo;。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.sinchew.com.my/pad/con/content_2086389.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sinchew.com.my%2Fpad%2Fcon%2Fcontent_2086389.html&d=4e%2FpP7P6HSNE6mjGPWQpDcZCnWmYDHHppvVe94ioujI%3D&h=3af6e5d4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.sinchew.com.my/pad/con/content_2086389.html</a>"},{"pid":"be4f8bb1c2f6128fe41f3a52bb5f00f312128721","tid":1331959,"uid":143093,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T06:41:55.000Z","msg":"RIP🙏🏻"},{"pid":"bd71b8dcd30bc9b793dac194a86418faf8196bbb","tid":1331959,"uid":35221,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"be4f8bb1c2f6128fe41f3a52bb5f00f312128721","tid":1331959,"uid":143093,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T06:41:55.000Z","msg":"RIP🙏🏻"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T06:42:29.000Z","msg":"上海灘七大歌后全部作古<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你都竟然識得姚莉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"391cfe6846fced792b60e226feb3800a73a03e07","tid":1331959,"uid":143093,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bd71b8dcd30bc9b793dac194a86418faf8196bbb","tid":1331959,"uid":35221,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"be4f8bb1c2f6128fe41f3a52bb5f00f312128721","tid":1331959,"uid":143093,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T06:41:55.000Z","msg":"RIP🙏🏻"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T06:42:29.000Z","msg":"上海灘七大歌后全部作古<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你都竟然識得姚莉<img 